<plot>This is the first time these people have been filmed by a non indigenous person ever. A journey into the unknown Benjamin Johns, DOP Robert Shacklady and Ayesha Celis were in the remote mountains of central Mexico for only 9 days. What they filmed with no prior permission gives a unique insight into a tribe who's Shamanic way of life has been unchanged for 1000's of years.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?402554</url></doc>
